title: Los Angeles prosecutors reviewing case against Bill Cosby
text: > Entertainment Los Angeles prosecutors reviewing case against Bill Cosby FILE - In this Friday, Nov. 21, 2014 file photo, comedian Bill Cosby performs at the Maxwell C. King Center for the Performing Arts, in Melbourne, Fla. Los Angeles prosecutors said Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015, that police had presented the results of their investigation into model Chloe Goinsâ€™ accusations that Cosby drugged and accosted her in a bedroom of the Playboy Mansion in August 2008. There is no timetable for when prosecutors will determine whether to file a case against the comedian. (AP Photo/Phelan M. Ebenhack, File)
